{"tid":1415572,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我地要多返啲和理非行動","createTime":"2019-08-05T13:54:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T16:53:22.000Z","uid":25643,"like":110,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"085b7f94b1b6cca4199b67910d9e4859a19042e3","tid":1415572,"uid":25643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:54:27.000Z","msg":"之前嘅各區放映會，而家唔見曬<br />\n之前好成功connect 說服咗好多淺藍居民<br />\n勇武當然都要繼續做<br />\n但唔好差唔多日日都開大片，無時間做和理非揼石仔<br />\n<br />\n唔可以畀政府分化走我哋嘅新支持者<br />\n我哋已經成手牌，要急住showhand 嘅係政府<br />\n我地要緊記  暴力邊緣論   <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1246915/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1246915/page/1</a>  <br />\n唔可以有機會令市民覺得我哋過咗火位<br />\n<br />\n升級武力係冇問題，但要循序漸進<br />\n勇武和理非交替，先可以令保守嘅香港人慢慢接受<br />\n勿忘 <strong>梁天琦致香港人的信：懇請不要被仇恨支配自己</strong><br />\n嚟緊我哋拎返起冷落咗一排嘅傳單，projector<br />\n重新走入社區同街坊解說鞏固佢哋信念<br />\n只有我哋同心協力，先可以打贏呢場硬仗<br />\n時代革命，光復香港"},{"pid":"613e774316e0a5c2413bdfbe142468971fc5d203","tid":1415572,"uid":25643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:55:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04e7e1fc171e2a338b56da0ab952536ccabc618e","tid":1415572,"uid":25643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:56:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0d07075d2e3464506a5bbdb94af1695394a701f","tid":1415572,"uid":25643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:57:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9646e0c3a54b984309e31fd24f49e67bff166768","tid":1415572,"uid":25643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:58:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0ddb5d17f01a5b6d9fb06b539485831379ab43b","tid":1415572,"uid":157891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:59:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pi